text: Dalbergia yunnanensis is a plant species of the genus Dalbergia: which is placed in the subfamily Faboideae and tribe Dalbergieae. == Subspecies == The Catalogue of Life lists: * D. yunnanensis var. collettii (Prain) Thoth. * D. yunnanensis var. yunnanensis Franch. == References == Thothathri K (1987) Taxonomic Revision of the Tribe Dalbergieae in the Indian...
